{"tid":414374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"主題：廣州地鐵 Apple Pay 入閘  仲煩過港女搭地鐵","createTime":"2017-09-26T07:33:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T09:54:35.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2a1b886099052c753aa0d6080c635c144cc455aa","tid":414374,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T07:33:38.000Z","msg":"昨日我們報導過新推出的 iPhone 8、iPhone 8 Plus 和 iPhone X，還有 Apple Watch Series 3 都支援 FeliCa 系統，技術上可以支援八達通卡，乘客有機會將八達通卡導入手機或手錶使用。正當香港人還在討論，八達通公司何時會作出支援，廣州地鐵今日起就支持 Apple Pay 付款入閘。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://timg.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2017-09/26/209133/uniqlo_1_5152ce609a69f75a9a074f796b3fe88c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftimg.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2017-09%2F26%2F209133%2Funiqlo_1_5152ce609a69f75a9a074f796b3fe88c.jpg&h=7a46288b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廣州地鐵昨日發佈公告，宣佈由 9 月 26 日開始，乘客可以利用 Apple Pay 過閘機，而且還不但支援新上市的 iPhone 8、iPhone 8 Plus 和 Apple Watch Series 3，就連 iPhone 6、iPhone 6s、iPhone 6 Plus、iPhone 6s Plus、iPhone 7、iPhone 7 Plus、iPhone SE 和前兩代的 Apple Watch 都通通支援。究竟點可以做到呢？不是說了支援 FeliCa 只有新版 iPhone 和日本上市的 iPhone 7 和 iPhone 7 Plus 嗎？<br />\n<br />\n原來廣州地鐵使用一般 Apple Pay 消費找數的方式，即是乘客每次入閘前都需要以指紋認證。首先 iPhone 或 Apple Watch 需要綁定銀聯信用卡，在入閘前開啟 iPhone，將上半部靠近閘機讀卡區，選擇用來支付車費的銀行卡，然後再以手指放在 Touch ID 上驗證指紋。相比起來，Apple Watch 反而比較簡單，只需選擇支付的銀行卡，再將手錶放近讀卡區，聽到聲響就可以入閘。搭廣州地鐵用 iPhone 入閘要先開 Apple Pay、揀銀行卡，再認證指紋，隨時比港女將手袋起勢捽地鐵入閘機仲麻煩同浪費時間。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4544/209133/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4544%2F209133%2F1%2F&d=hq1Tv1DQFqCq6TPm3S9dwgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=23201c2b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4544/209133/1/</a>"},{"pid":"d1e20e277d42b4cdb5500eb279d9f43aad3edcb4","tid":414374,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T07:36:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cd3320cc9c5a19d789fd04944aaf6c63f073479","tid":414374,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T07:36:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29f6a298f287e6802825bd17fbc39f72a8f98690","tid":414374,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T07:37:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e89fe76c752c16409922b80dd6b7bf949a8d9b00","tid":414374,"uid":59536,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T07:39:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又標籤我哋港女<br />\n黐撚線，我入閘勁撚快㗎囉</blockquote><br />\n你肥婆 點同港女比<br />\n人地過左閘 你仲係個閘到啊<br />\n肥閪"},{"pid":"e7f87d3202a201deb0c6944fcbf95cb28b193823","tid":414374,"uid":90766,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T07:39:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又標籤我哋港女<br />\n黐撚線，我入閘勁撚快㗎囉</blockquote><br />\n你太肥入唔到閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57fee632f67bf91dfbe24d072046817bbb131e36","tid":414374,"uid":5686,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T07:40:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭廣州地鐵用 iPhone 入閘要先開 Apple Pay、揀銀行卡，再認證指紋，隨時比港女將手袋起勢捽地鐵入閘機仲麻煩同浪費時間。<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n件事本身只係放手指係Touch ID 上面, 再隊部機埋出Sensor 再出閘。<br />\n<br />\n點解可以俾佢講到咁多步驟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea3ab6e2e5ff88bbace487d741844f266cf6c15","tid":414374,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T07:42:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"016d9679d91855274e1b1d714b60205450122f2e","tid":414374,"uid":90766,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T07:44:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>又標籤我哋港女<br />\n黐撚線，我入閘勁撚快㗎囉</blockquote><br />\n你肥婆 點同港女比<br />\n人地過左閘 你仲係個閘到啊<br />\n肥閪</blockquote><br />\n文盲？<br />\n我過得勁快喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n緊係快啦，成個閘都比你撞開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"